name: Click For Money
description:
Do you want to try planting a tree and experience the feeling of a rich man?
This is an excellent and interesting game of getting rich!


With this game, you can become the richest capitalist of all time！
Plant a tree that belongs to you,make your pocket rich and cultivate the richest wood in the world in the tree planting app!
Click to make the tree grow and get more rewards for you, just like real capitalists get more rewards!
Plant a tree that belongs to you, click to let nature give feedback, rich growth in this game, become more expensive!


In the process of planting tree, you can also use rain props or fertilize to make the plants grow faster.
Get ready to download Click For Money and plant your own tree!
You are only one step away from becoming rich!
